Dialogue: 0,0:01:32.13,0:01:34.86,main arial top 20,XY,0000,0000,0000,,Well, we've come across quite the obstacle.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:32.25,0:01:37.02,Episode Title,Eptitle Sign,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(500,500)}Episode 5  "The Sword Devil, Shā Wú Shēng"
Dialogue: 0,0:01:34.86,0:01:38.01,main arial top 20,XY,0000,0000,0000,,Our best chance of reaching the summit\Nof the Demon Spine Mountains
Dialogue: 0,0:01:38.01,0:01:42.37,main arial 20,XY,0000,0000,0000,,has fallen into the hands of the \Nmost dangerous person imaginable.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:42.37,0:01:45.48,main arial 20,DF,0000,0000,0000,,But just who is this man?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:46.66,0:01:49.48,main arial 20,SY,0000,0000,0000,,I suppose a Hù Yìn Shī who has \Nspent her whole life on sacred ground
Dialogue: 0,0:01:49.87,0:01:52.55,main arial 20,SY,0000,0000,0000,,wouldn't know about someone so infamous.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:53.05,0:01:55.36,main arial 20,XY,0000,0000,0000,,He is Shā Wú Shēng,
Dialogue: 0,0:01:55.36,0:01:58.90,main arial 20,XY,0000,0000,0000,,a swordsman also known by his title \Nof the Screaming Phoenix Killer.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:59.37,0:02:00.98,main arial 20,XY,0000,0000,0000,,He makes his living as an assassin,
Dialogue: 0,0:02:00.98,0:02:05.93,main arial 20,XY,0000,0000,0000,,and is considered greatest \Nkiller in the underworld.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:06.56,0:02:09.12,main arial 20,SB,0000,0000,0000,,And why's this guy hate you?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:09.12,0:02:12.17,main arial 20,XH,0000,0000,0000,,If you gathered together\Neveryone who hated this man,
Dialogue: 0,0:02:12.17,0:02:15.50,main arial 20,XH,0000,0000,0000,,you could hold a parade.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:16.58,0:02:20.11,main arial 20,XH,0000,0000,0000,,And I am included among \Nthat number, of course.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:20.11,0:02:23.72,main arial 20,SB,0000,0000,0000,,Whoa, now, I thought you two had made up?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:23.72,0:02:26.41,main arial 20,XH,0000,0000,0000,,Our aligned interests take precedence now.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:26.41,0:02:31.73,main arial 20,XH,0000,0000,0000,,But unfortunately, not all consider the Tiān \NXing Jiàn to be as significant as I do.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:32.25,0:02:35.94,main arial 20,XH,0000,0000,0000,,I doubt we have anything we can use \Nto bargain with Shā Wú Shēng.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:36.35,0:02:38.45,main arial 20,DF,0000,0000,0000,,If this grudge is so intense,
Dialogue: 0,0:02:38.45,0:02:43.00,main arial 20,DF,0000,0000,0000,,would it be difficult to convince \Nhim to hand the flute over after all?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:43.47,0:02:46.81,main arial 20,JC,0000,0000,0000,,Hey, come on, why's everyone \Nbeing so spineless about this?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:46.81,0:02:50.28,main arial 20,JC,0000,0000,0000,,This guy stole the Soul Echo Flute \Nfrom Mister Guǐ Niǎo's master, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:50.28,0:02:53.41,main arial 20,JC,0000,0000,0000,,That means we just take it back!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:53.79,0:02:56.19,main arial 20,XH,0000,0000,0000,,Why did you stop us, anyway?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:56.19,0:02:59.21,main arial 20,XH,0000,0000,0000,,Even if he is the Screaming Phoenix Killer,
Dialogue: 0,0:02:59.21,0:03:03.76,main arial 20,XH,0000,0000,0000,,I think this group attacking together \Nwould have stood a fine chance.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:03.76,0:03:08.97,main arial 20,JC,0000,0000,0000,,Even though there was one \Nguy shaking in his boots!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:10.09,0:03:15.25,main arial 20,XY,0000,0000,0000,,There was a chance of victory, \Nbut not a certain one.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:15.25,0:03:19.74,main arial 20,XY,0000,0000,0000,,More than that, our goal is \Nnot to defeat Shā Wú Shēng.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:19.74,0:03:23.09,main arial 20,XY,0000,0000,0000,,We need to cross the Valley of the \NDead and the Valley of the Doll,
Dialogue: 0,0:03:23.09,0:03:24.47,main arial 20,XY,0000,0000,0000,,and to ensure that,
Dialogue: 0,0:03:24.47,0:03:28.09,main arial 20,XY,0000,0000,0000,,Xíng Hài and your master must reach \Nthe Demon Spine Mountains in one piece.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:28.09,0:03:31.16,main arial 20,XY,0000,0000,0000,,We can't risk them being injured en route.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:31.16,0:03:34.19,main arial 20,JC,0000,0000,0000,,So as long as my bro Shòu
Dialogue: 0,0:03:34.19,0:03:37.34,main arial 20,JC,0000,0000,0000,,and the demon aren't hurt, it works out?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:39.19,0:03:41.59,main arial 20,SY,0000,0000,0000,,What are you getting at, Juǎn?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:41.59,0:03:42.68,main arial 20,JC,0000,0000,0000,,I hate to admit it,
Dialogue: 0,0:03:42.68,0:03:46.30,main arial 20,JC,0000,0000,0000,,but I don't have any big jobs to do on\Nour trek up the Demon Spine Mountains.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:46.30,0:03:50.70,main arial 20,JC,0000,0000,0000,,So if we just wager my\Nlife to get the Soul Echo Flute,
Dialogue: 0,0:03:50.70,0:03:52.40,main arial 20,JC,0000,0000,0000,,there's no problem, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:52.72,0:03:56.11,main arial 20,XY,0000,0000,0000,,You intend to battle Shā Wú Shēng alone?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:56.33,0:03:56.99,main arial 20,SB,0000,0000,0000,,Wha—?!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:56.99,0:03:59.14,main arial 20,SB,0000,0000,0000,,Hey! Don't be stupid!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:59.44,0:04:01.31,main arial 20,JC,0000,0000,0000,,So what I'm stupid!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:01.31,0:04:04.28,main arial 20,JC,0000,0000,0000,,But this is a once-in-a-lifetime \Nchance for me.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:04.28,0:04:07.98,main arial 20,JC,0000,0000,0000,,If I'm the one to defeat the \NScreaming Phoenix Killer,
Dialogue: 0,0:04:07.98,0:04:10.75,main arial 20,JC,0000,0000,0000,,my name will be heard throughout the land!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:12.40,0:04:16.17,main arial 20,SB,0000,0000,0000,,And if it doesn't work out \Nthat way, you'll be dead, kid.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:16.17,0:04:17.40,main arial 20,JC,0000,0000,0000,,Dead?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:18.22,0:04:21.64,main arial 20,JC,0000,0000,0000,,I don't exactly have a \Nlife to forsake, anyway.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:21.64,0:04:26.77,main arial 20,JC,0000,0000,0000,,To be out in the world with no reputation is\Npractically the same as not having been born.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:27.44,0:04:32.95,main arial 20,SB,0000,0000,0000,,Can't you see how you and I are both here?\NEating, talking, and being alive?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:32.95,0:04:37.46,main arial 20,JC,0000,0000,0000,,And maybe if I was as old as you,\NI'd have given up, too.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:37.46,0:04:41.02,main arial 20,JC,0000,0000,0000,,But there's no way I'll be satisfied \Nwith a life of just that.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:41.83,0:04:46.29,main arial 20,DF,0000,0000,0000,,But fighting alone seems... too reckless.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:46.88,0:04:52.20,main arial 20,JC,0000,0000,0000,,Hey, I can tell how good someone is \Nfrom having felt his sword firsthand!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:52.81,0:04:55.64,main arial 20,JC,0000,0000,0000,,Bottom line is, the guy's slowing down.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:56.12,0:05:00.49,main arial 20,JC,0000,0000,0000,,His reputation as #1 in the \Nunderworld is old news, isn't it?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:00.49,0:05:05.49,main arial 20,JC,0000,0000,0000,,He might've scared me a bit at first glance,\Nbut I've got him figured out now.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:05.49,0:05:06.91,main arial 20,JC,0000,0000,0000,,I can take him!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:07.24,0:05:11.65,main arial 20,SB,0000,0000,0000,,Hey, can't you talk some sense \Ninto your stupid student?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:11.65,0:05:16.41,main arial 20,SY,0000,0000,0000,,When he gets like this,\Nthere's no getting through to him.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:16.41,0:05:17.39,main arial 20,SY,0000,0000,0000,,It's a waste of time.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:18.17,0:05:20.42,main arial 20,SB,0000,0000,0000,,Some mentor you are.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:21.30,0:05:24.47,main arial 20,XY,0000,0000,0000,,What you're proposing is \Nessentially a gamble.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:24.47,0:05:29.36,main arial 20,XY,0000,0000,0000,,Personally, I'd rather handle this \Nmatter with a more practical approach.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:29.36,0:05:33.33,main arial 20,XY,0000,0000,0000,,Let's wait until tomorrow morning\N to confront Shā Wú Shēng.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:33.33,0:05:37.44,main arial 20,XY,0000,0000,0000,,I will spend the night seeing \Nif there's a preferable alternative.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:37.92,0:05:41.64,main arial 20,XY,0000,0000,0000,,If I come up with nothing,\NI'll leave it to you.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:41.64,0:05:44.00,main arial 20,XH,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, I know!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:44.00,0:05:49.65,main arial 20,XH,0000,0000,0000,,There's a spell that turn the\Nblood of a corpse to acid,
Dialogue: 0,0:05:49.65,0:05:51.13,main arial 20,XH,0000,0000,0000,,then makes it burst forth.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:51.62,0:05:55.63,main arial 20,XH,0000,0000,0000,,Why not cast it on him while he still lives?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:55.63,0:05:58.86,main arial 20,XH,0000,0000,0000,,Then, once he's killed,
Dialogue: 0,0:05:58.86,0:06:02.63,main arial 20,XH,0000,0000,0000,,both he and his foe\Nwill be melted into nothing!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:02.63,0:06:05.53,main arial 20,JC,0000,0000,0000,,How about we skip the suicide attacks?!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:06.17,0:06:09.14,main arial 20,DF,0000,0000,0000,,If Sir Guǐ Niǎo is unable\Nto come up with anything,
Dialogue: 0,0:06:09.14,0:06:12.25,main arial 20,DF,0000,0000,0000,,we will truly be out of options.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:12.98,0:06:17.03,main arial 20,DF,0000,0000,0000,,Should it come to that, I will \Nfight at Sir Juǎn's side.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:17.03,0:06:18.78,main arial 20,SB,0000,0000,0000,,H-Hey!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:19.03,0:06:21.00,main arial 20,JC,0000,0000,0000,,Seriously?!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:21.00,0:06:22.38,main arial 20,JC,0000,0000,0000,,For me?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:22.38,0:06:24.39,main arial 20,DF,0000,0000,0000,,What in the world do you mean?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:24.39,0:06:28.35,main arial 20,DF,0000,0000,0000,,The Soul Echo Flute is indispensable in \Nretrieving the Tiān Xing Jiàn's handle.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:28.35,0:06:33.97,main arial 20,DF,0000,0000,0000,,It's not only been stolen, but if there's \Nno other means to retrieve it...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:33.97,0:06:36.82,main arial 20,DF,0000,0000,0000,,I must be willing to accept \Nany fate to ensure its return.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:36.82,0:06:39.56,main arial 20,JC,0000,0000,0000,,Y-You're right!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:39.56,0:06:41.68,main arial 20,JC,0000,0000,0000,,I totally understand!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:41.68,0:06:45.30,main arial 20,JC,0000,0000,0000,,But I'm gonna take out that \NScreaming Phoenix Killer bastard!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:45.30,0:06:47.52,main arial 20,SB,0000,0000,0000,,Dammit, I'm through listening to this!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:47.52,0:06:48.94,main arial 20,SB,0000,0000,0000,,Do whatever you want.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:53.17,0:06:54.67,main arial 20,JC,0000,0000,0000,,Man, what's with him?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:54.67,0:06:58.35,main arial 20,JC,0000,0000,0000,,He needs the Soul Echo Flute to make \Nit to Seven Sins Tower, too!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:58.35,0:07:01.58,main arial 20,DF,0000,0000,0000,,Sir Shāng has his own \Nway of handling things.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:01.58,0:07:03.99,main arial 20,DF,0000,0000,0000,,We can't expect him to act \Naccording to our perspective.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:05.62,0:07:09.96,main arial 20,XY,0000,0000,0000,,Again, just to remind you,\Ndo not act until tomorrow morning.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:09.96,0:07:13.21,main arial 20,XY,0000,0000,0000,,I want some time to consider this.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:13.21,0:07:17.85,main arial 20,XY,0000,0000,0000,,I'd like confronting Shā Wú Shēng \Ndirectly to be our last resort.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:17.85,0:07:19.38,main arial 20,JC,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah, yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:19.38,0:07:24.74,main arial 20,XH,0000,0000,0000,,I can prepare a variety of \Nnightmarish spells as well.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:25.08,0:07:28.58,main arial 20,,0000,0000,0000,,Come and see me first thing in the morning.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:28.61,0:07:31.25,main arial 20,JC,0000,0000,0000,,I'm gonna respectfully decline, thanks!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:45.76,0:07:46.90,main arial 20,SW,0000,0000,0000,,I thought as much.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:48.16,0:07:51.78,main arial 20,SW,0000,0000,0000,,I knew you'd be the one to come.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:58.35,0:08:02.71,main arial 20,SB,0000,0000,0000,,One of my comrades intends to pick a \Nfight with you first thing tomorrow morning.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:02.71,0:08:05.91,main arial 20,SB,0000,0000,0000,,And he actually thinks he stands a chance.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:05.91,0:08:08.99,main arial 20,SW,0000,0000,0000,,How very gallant of him.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:08.99,0:08:12.23,main arial 20,SB,0000,0000,0000,,It's your fault for playing around.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:12.23,0:08:15.77,main arial 20,SB,0000,0000,0000,,You were taking it easy on him \Nat the temple, weren't you?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:15.77,0:08:18.70,main arial 20,SB,0000,0000,0000,,So he would underestimate you.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:18.70,0:08:21.84,main arial 20,SW,0000,0000,0000,,I'm afraid that I don't know\Nwhat you're talking about.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:24.86,0:08:27.91,main arial 20,SB,0000,0000,0000,,You made the whole situation \Nmore complicated on purpose!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:27.91,0:08:29.76,main arial 20,SB,0000,0000,0000,,You wanna kill people that badly?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:29.76,0:08:32.97,main arial 20,SW,0000,0000,0000,,You'd ask me, of all people, that question?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:32.97,0:08:36.51,main arial 20,SW,0000,0000,0000,,Have you not heard that I am called \Nthe Screaming Phoenix Killer?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:36.75,0:08:41.05,main arial 20,SB,0000,0000,0000,,Sure haven't. Apparently you're \Na pretty big deal, though.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:46.66,0:08:47.96,main arial 20,SB,0000,0000,0000,,What's so funny?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:48.25,0:08:51.38,main arial 20,SW,0000,0000,0000,,Well, I can't help but feel a bit amused.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:51.38,0:08:55.56,main arial 20,SW,0000,0000,0000,,It's been a while since I've had anyone \Nelse sit across from me at a table.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:55.99,0:08:58.93,main arial 20,SB,0000,0000,0000,,Do people consider you hard\Nto get along with, pal?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:59.38,0:09:02.39,main arial 20,SW,0000,0000,0000,,I suppose I've made too \Nmuch of a name of myself.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:02.39,0:09:04.00,main arial 20,SW,0000,0000,0000,,Usually...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:04.00,0:09:08.63,main arial 20,SW,0000,0000,0000,,This place would be full of \Nlively customers, even at this hour.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:09.12,0:09:13.65,main arial 20,SW,0000,0000,0000,,But when word gets out that the Screaming \NPhoenix Killer is in the area,
Dialogue: 0,0:09:13.65,0:09:15.12,main arial 20,SW,0000,0000,0000,,this happens.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:15.12,0:09:17.88,main arial 20,SB,0000,0000,0000,,I'm surprised you didn't get thrown out.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:17.88,0:09:21.79,main arial 20,SW,0000,0000,0000,,The owner doesn't have the \Nnerve to complain to me.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:21.79,0:09:26.93,main arial 20,SW,0000,0000,0000,,I show some compassion by paying for \Nthe time I've been here, at least.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:27.78,0:09:31.23,main arial 20,SB,0000,0000,0000,,If people hate you when \Nyou're that considerate,
Dialogue: 0,0:09:31.23,0:09:34.60,main arial 20,SB,0000,0000,0000,,you must be known for \Nsome real nasty business.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:36.15,0:09:39.99,main arial 20,SW,0000,0000,0000,,I'd think that if you'd heard\Nany of the tales about me,
Dialogue: 0,0:09:39.99,0:09:44.35,main arial 20,SW,0000,0000,0000,,you wouldn't have risked\Ntalking to me like this.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:44.35,0:09:46.92,main arial 20,SB,0000,0000,0000,,Well, I'm a traveler, you know?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:46.92,0:09:49.11,main arial 20,SB,0000,0000,0000,,I haven't been in this country for long.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:49.90,0:09:51.58,main arial 20,SW,0000,0000,0000,,Where are you from, then?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:51.86,0:09:53.52,main arial 20,SB,0000,0000,0000,,Xī Yōu.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:54.09,0:09:55.61,main arial 20,SW,0000,0000,0000,,Xī Yōu...?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:56.14,0:09:58.89,main arial 20,SW,0000,0000,0000,,On the other side of the \NWasteland of Spirits?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:59.36,0:10:01.05,main arial 20,SB,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah, that's the one.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:05.62,0:10:09.97,main arial 20,SW,0000,0000,0000,,If you're joking,\Nit'd be funnier if you said
Dialogue: 0,0:10:09.97,0:10:13.04,main arial 20,SW,0000,0000,0000,,you swam upstream from the afterlife.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:13.53,0:10:18.77,main arial 20,SW,0000,0000,0000,,How could you have crossed \Nthat accursed wilderness?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:19.25,0:10:22.11,main arial 20,SB,0000,0000,0000,,With the two legs I was born with.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:23.25,0:10:25.75,main arial 20,SW,0000,0000,0000,,Well, that has to be a joke.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:26.35,0:10:28.65,main arial 20,SW,0000,0000,0000,,No human could manage that.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:29.37,0:10:30.89,main arial 20,SB,0000,0000,0000,,Well, I'll admit,
Dialogue: 0,0:10:30.89,0:10:35.56,main arial 20,SB,0000,0000,0000,,it's a miracle that I made\Nit with both legs intact.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:36.29,0:10:41.83,main arial 20,SW,0000,0000,0000,,If what you say is true, it makes\Nsense that you wouldn't know my name.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:42.70,0:10:47.53,main arial 20,SW,0000,0000,0000,,I've never met someone from Xī Yōu, either.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:48.15,0:10:50.23,main arial 20,SB,0000,0000,0000,,Look, who cares about me?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:50.23,0:10:54.73,main arial 20,SB,0000,0000,0000,,I wanna talk about the Soul Echo \NFlute that you've got right now.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:54.73,0:10:55.90,main arial 20,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:57.43,0:11:01.70,main arial 20,SB,0000,0000,0000,,I don't know what happened \Nwith you and Guǐ Niǎo,
Dialogue: 0,0:11:01.70,0:11:05.25,main arial 20,SB,0000,0000,0000,,but I'm asking you to find another \Nway to settle your vendetta with him.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:06.40,0:11:07.71,main arial 20,SW,0000,0000,0000,,Guǐ Niǎo...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:10.49,0:11:13.63,main arial 20,SW,0000,0000,0000,,So that's what he calls himself now?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:14.59,0:11:15.96,main arial 20,SB,0000,0000,0000,,How about it?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:15.53,0:11:26.69,sign_20247_150_Devilwood_Flower,Sign,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(1,5866)}Devilwood\NFlower\NGarden
Dialogue: 0,0:11:15.96,0:11:20.78,main arial 20,SW,0000,0000,0000,,The man's ability to escape\Nme is almost god-like.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:21.26,0:11:28.72,main arial 20,SW,0000,0000,0000,,To ensure his death, I need something \Nthat forces him to cross paths with me.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:29.14,0:11:31.01,main arial 20,SW,0000,0000,0000,,That brought me to this flute.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:31.01,0:11:34.78,main arial 20,SW,0000,0000,0000,,And I see no reason to give up \Nmy trump card after finally acquiring it.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:35.18,0:11:38.55,main arial 20,SB,0000,0000,0000,,But that flute has a more important use.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:38.55,0:11:40.82,main arial 20,SB,0000,0000,0000,,Something that has nothing to do with you.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:41.89,0:11:43.94,main arial 20,SW,0000,0000,0000,,I have a more pressing question.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:44.74,0:11:46.56,main arial 20,SW,0000,0000,0000,,Did you really come here
Dialogue: 0,0:11:46.56,0:11:51.27,main arial 20,SW,0000,0000,0000,,thinking that you could\Nsettle this with words?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:01.81,0:12:03.66,main arial 20,SW,0000,0000,0000,,I thought not.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:03.66,0:12:06.18,main arial 20,SW,0000,0000,0000,,Anyone who would have nodded at that...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:06.68,0:12:10.95,main arial 20,SW,0000,0000,0000,,Also would have lost their head long ago.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:11.40,0:12:13.22,main arial 20,SB,0000,0000,0000,,Don't be so scary, man.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:13.58,0:12:16.46,main arial 20,SW,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, but it's the truth...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:17.22,0:12:18.57,main arial 20,SW,0000,0000,0000,,If I'm being honest,
Dialogue: 0,0:12:18.57,0:12:21.23,main arial 20,SW,0000,0000,0000,,I've been thinking about nothing...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:21.23,0:12:25.03,main arial 20,SW,0000,0000,0000,,But killing you since you sat down.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:25.49,0:12:30.03,main arial 20,SW,0000,0000,0000,,I've been watching, intently, \Nfor the perfect opportunity
Dialogue: 0,0:12:30.03,0:12:32.84,main arial 20,SW,0000,0000,0000,,to decapitate you in one stroke.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:46.45,0:12:48.20,main arial 20,SB,0000,0000,0000,,You're damned crazy.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:49.21,0:12:51.69,main arial 20,SW,0000,0000,0000,,You're one to talk...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:52.26,0:12:57.89,main arial 20,SW,0000,0000,0000,,No normal man would be on guard well enough \Nto avoid death at my hands this long.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:58.94,0:13:01.17,main arial 20,SW,0000,0000,0000,,You speak peacefully enough...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:01.90,0:13:06.87,main arial 20,SW,0000,0000,0000,,But are prepared for\Nany attack I could imagine.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:21.80,0:13:24.96,main arial 20,SW,0000,0000,0000,,You brazenly claim to want \Nto discuss the matter,
Dialogue: 0,0:13:24.96,0:13:31.03,main arial 20,SW,0000,0000,0000,,but you've been sitting there with a \Nmindset like a drawn blade all along.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:33.48,0:13:37.76,main arial 20,SW,0000,0000,0000,,I'm pleased to finally encounter \Nsomeone who knows what they're doing.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:37.76,0:13:43.84,main arial 20,SW,0000,0000,0000,,Maybe your claim of crossing the Wasteland \Nof Spirits isn't a lie after all.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:45.52,0:13:47.81,main arial 20,SB,0000,0000,0000,,You're saying that while we've been drinking,
Dialogue: 0,0:13:48.25,0:13:51.65,main arial 20,SB,0000,0000,0000,,we've already been fighting each other?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:51.65,0:13:57.70,main arial 20,SW,0000,0000,0000,,Only amateurs think battles\Nbegin after swords are drawn.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:58.44,0:14:02.49,main arial 20,SW,0000,0000,0000,,Belief that bloodlust marks the beginning\Nin turn marks you as second-rate.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:03.13,0:14:07.62,main arial 20,SB,0000,0000,0000,,I haven't decided whether \NI'm gonna fight you yet.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:07.62,0:14:10.49,main arial 20,SW,0000,0000,0000,,The path of the sword is \None of inevitability.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:11.10,0:14:13.04,main arial 20,SW,0000,0000,0000,,Your battle against those who
Dialogue: 0,0:14:13.04,0:14:16.20,main arial 20,SW,0000,0000,0000,,you will cut down begins the \Nmoment you cross paths with them.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:16.20,0:14:19.38,main arial 20,SW,0000,0000,0000,,Only those aware of that \Nare truly first-rate.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:20.47,0:14:25.38,main arial 20,SB,0000,0000,0000,,And that's first rate? Sounds like those \Nguys are just going with the flow.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:25.38,0:14:28.73,main arial 20,SW,0000,0000,0000,,Trying to deny an inevitable fate is the
Dialogue: 0,0:14:28.73,0:14:32.43,main arial 20,SW,0000,0000,0000,,act of a fool who can not \Nsee what their fate entails.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:32.43,0:14:37.36,main arial 20,SB,0000,0000,0000,,I'm not drawing my\Nsword unless I'm convinced...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:37.69,0:14:39.79,main arial 20,SB,0000,0000,0000,,that either you or I need to die.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:40.38,0:14:44.18,main arial 20,SW,0000,0000,0000,,Then you can leave right now.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:44.81,0:14:49.84,main arial 20,SW,0000,0000,0000,,And I will just kill the imbeciles \Nthat call upon me in the morning.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:58.32,0:15:00.94,main arial 20,SW,0000,0000,0000,,An aversion to bloodshed...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:00.94,0:15:04.91,main arial 20,SW,0000,0000,0000,,That's a tendency your type always has.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:04.91,0:15:07.92,main arial 20,SW,0000,0000,0000,,And that makes this \Nconflict an inevitability.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:13.91,0:15:15.13,main arial 20,SW,0000,0000,0000,,You've known...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:15.13,0:15:21.34,main arial 20,SW,0000,0000,0000,,that you'd have to draw your blade\Nfrom the moment you laid eyes on me.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:21.34,0:15:25.81,main arial 20,SW,0000,0000,0000,,You just came here to give yourself \Nan excuse for when it happens.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:25.81,0:15:27.79,main arial 20,SW,0000,0000,0000,,Talk things over?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:27.79,0:15:30.94,main arial 20,SW,0000,0000,0000,,Don't lie to yourself with \Nsuch a hollow pretense.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:32.29,0:15:35.01,main arial 20,SB,0000,0000,0000,,Don't you ever have any doubts?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:35.01,0:15:37.33,main arial 20,SB,0000,0000,0000,,Or hesitate, for fear of making a mistake?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:37.33,0:15:38.71,main arial 20,SW,0000,0000,0000,,Never.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:39.23,0:15:42.92,main arial 20,SW,0000,0000,0000,,I have a simple method for clearing\Naway any doubts I may have.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:44.22,0:15:48.03,main arial 20,SW,0000,0000,0000,,The only thing that ever concerns me is
Dialogue: 0,0:15:48.03,0:15:53.36,main arial 20,SW,0000,0000,0000,,whether or not someone I've laid \Neyes on is worthy of my blade.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:54.26,0:15:56.94,main arial 20,SW,0000,0000,0000,,And the moment after I raise that question,
Dialogue: 0,0:15:56.94,0:16:00.69,main arial 20,SW,0000,0000,0000,,I find a corpse at my feet.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:01.16,0:16:04.36,main arial 20,SW,0000,0000,0000,,And so, in the 15 years since \NI've mastered the sword,
Dialogue: 0,0:16:04.36,0:16:07.98,main arial 20,SW,0000,0000,0000,,I have never been troubled by doubt.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:13.84,0:16:15.23,main arial 20,SW,0000,0000,0000,,You drew it...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:15.89,0:16:17.32,main arial 20,SB,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:17.32,0:16:20.63,main arial 20,SB,0000,0000,0000,,Who should live? The idiot who's \Ntrying his hardest in life,
Dialogue: 0,0:16:20.63,0:16:24.34,main arial 20,SB,0000,0000,0000,,or the bastard who could live \Nor die with little difference?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:24.34,0:16:27.00,main arial 20,SB,0000,0000,0000,,That question helped me make up my mind.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:27.31,0:16:32.01,main arial 20,SW,0000,0000,0000,,Such mental detours \Nwill only dull your blade...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:32.44,0:16:37.34,main arial 20,SW,0000,0000,0000,,If you want to win, you need to deal \Nwith fate in more concise terms.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:39.80,0:16:43.14,main arial 20,SB,0000,0000,0000,,I don't give a damn about fate.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:43.14,0:16:45.96,main arial 20,SB,0000,0000,0000,,I choose when to draw it and when to strike.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:46.72,0:16:49.15,main arial 20,SB,0000,0000,0000,,That's my sword!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:51.65,0:16:57.15,main arial 20,SW,0000,0000,0000,,One last question: have you ever \Nheard the title "Enigmatic Gale"?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:57.15,0:16:58.74,main arial 20,SB,0000,0000,0000,,I haven't.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:58.74,0:17:02.90,main arial 20,SB,0000,0000,0000,,Like I said, I'm not up to date on \Nlocal affairs here in Dōng Li.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:06.49,0:17:07.88,main arial 20,SW,0000,0000,0000,,I thought as much...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:08.33,0:17:12.57,main arial 20,SW,0000,0000,0000,,How sad. To dance to\Nhis tune with no idea...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:13.31,0:17:15.17,main arial 20,SB,0000,0000,0000,,What are you talking about?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:15.17,0:17:16.61,main arial 20,SW,0000,0000,0000,,Don't worry about it.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:16.61,0:17:21.72,main arial 20,SW,0000,0000,0000,,Besides, if you die here,\Nyou'll have no cause to regret it.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:50.71,0:17:55.85,main arial 20,XY,0000,0000,0000,,Good grief. Do the two of you have some \Nsort of grudge against chairs and tables?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:57.77,0:18:00.66,main arial 20,SW,0000,0000,0000,,Hallucinogenic smoke... Damn you again!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:01.92,0:18:05.09,main arial 20,SB,0000,0000,0000,,Guǐ Niǎo! Did you pull some \Nkind of weird trick again?!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:05.09,0:18:06.09,main arial 20,SB,0000,0000,0000,,What are you doing?!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:06.09,0:18:07.76,main arial 20,XY,0000,0000,0000,,I'm sorry. Weren't you the one talking
Dialogue: 0,0:18:07.76,0:18:11.33,main arial 20,XY,0000,0000,0000,,about how he'd rather avoid \Na fight to the death?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:11.33,0:18:13.37,main arial 20,SB,0000,0000,0000,,Uh... W-Well...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:13.74,0:18:17.62,main arial 20,XY,0000,0000,0000,,And you, Wú Shēng.\NI thought you were after me?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:17.62,0:18:20.96,main arial 20,XY,0000,0000,0000,,Don't go changing targets for no reason.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:21.73,0:18:26.95,main arial 20,SW,0000,0000,0000,,No matter what kind of illusions \Nyou use, you won't fool me again.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:27.54,0:18:30.76,main arial 20,SW,0000,0000,0000,,I have no intention of \Nletting this flute go!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:30.76,0:18:34.42,main arial 20,SW,0000,0000,0000,,And I will cut down anyone who approaches me!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:35.13,0:18:36.58,main arial 20,SW,0000,0000,0000,,So now what?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:36.58,0:18:38.46,main arial 20,SW,0000,0000,0000,,Think you can still escape me?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:38.85,0:18:42.26,main arial 20,XY,0000,0000,0000,,No, you can have the Soul Echo Flute.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:42.26,0:18:44.93,main arial 20,XY,0000,0000,0000,,It belonged to my master, \Nso take good care of it.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:46.10,0:18:50.17,main arial 20,XY,0000,0000,0000,,Now that I think about it, \Nno matter who holds it,
Dialogue: 0,0:18:50.17,0:18:54.78,main arial 20,XY,0000,0000,0000,,there's no problem as long as they guide \Nus through the Labyrinth of Darkness.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:54.78,0:18:58.40,main arial 20,XY,0000,0000,0000,,And luckily enough, you have some \Nskill at playing it. What do you say?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:58.40,0:19:02.04,main arial 20,XY,0000,0000,0000,,Care to join us on the trip \Nto the Demon Spine Mountains?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:02.04,0:19:04.75,main arial 20,SW,0000,0000,0000,,Are you absolutely insane?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:05.11,0:19:11.12,main arial 20,XY,0000,0000,0000,,If we make it through the Labyrinth of \NDarkness safely, I'll offer you my head.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:14.44,0:19:17.62,main arial 20,SW,0000,0000,0000,,That's quite the bold offer.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:17.62,0:19:22.94,main arial 20,SW,0000,0000,0000,,Does this matter involving the Tiān Xing \NJiàn really hold so much value to you?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:24.17,0:19:29.98,main arial 20,XY,0000,0000,0000,,I always make sure to complete any \Ntask I start. It's that simple.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:30.46,0:19:31.66,main arial 20,SW,0000,0000,0000,,So be it.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:32.09,0:19:33.84,main arial 20,SW,0000,0000,0000,,You've piqued my interest.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:33.84,0:19:37.11,main arial 20,SW,0000,0000,0000,,It might be interesting to visit the castle
Dialogue: 0,0:19:37.11,0:19:40.17,main arial 20,SW,0000,0000,0000,,that belongs to the\Ninfamous Bones of Creation.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:40.17,0:19:42.41,main arial 20,XY,0000,0000,0000,,Then prepare for a journey.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:42.41,0:19:44.96,main arial 20,XY,0000,0000,0000,,We meet at the dock tomorrow at noon.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:49.27,0:19:50.78,main arial 20,SB,0000,0000,0000,,Hey!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:50.78,0:19:52.86,main arial 20,SB,0000,0000,0000,,What in the hell?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:52.86,0:19:58.27,main arial 20,SW,0000,0000,0000,,Make your peace with your \Nhead during the journey.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:58.78,0:20:01.97,main arial 20,SW,0000,0000,0000,,Because when we reach the summit, \NI will be taking it from you.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:13.22,0:20:16.50,main arial 20,SB,0000,0000,0000,,What are you gonna do\Nabout making a promise like that?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:16.50,0:20:18.82,main arial 20,XY,0000,0000,0000,,I'll ponder that one as we go along.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:18.82,0:20:22.36,main arial 20,XY,0000,0000,0000,,I have until we exit the Labyrinth \Nof Darkness to figure out
Dialogue: 0,0:20:22.36,0:20:26.43,main arial 20,XY,0000,0000,0000,,if I really do need to \Npresent my head to him.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:26.43,0:20:30.11,main arial 20,XY,0000,0000,0000,,I might come across some \Ninspiration in the meantime.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:30.11,0:20:31.53,main arial 20,SB,0000,0000,0000,,You make it sound so damn easy.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:31.90,0:20:36.33,main arial 20,XY,0000,0000,0000,,In contrast, the matter of the Soul \NEcho Flute had to be solved tonight.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:36.33,0:20:41.39,main arial 20,XY,0000,0000,0000,,Rather... I had to take action \Nthe second you made your move.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:41.39,0:20:44.19,main arial 20,XY,0000,0000,0000,,So, with my hand forced,\Nthis was the option I was left with.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:44.19,0:20:46.31,main arial 20,XY,0000,0000,0000,,Desperate times and all that.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:46.31,0:20:48.80,main arial 20,SB,0000,0000,0000,,So should I have minded my own business?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:48.80,0:20:50.25,main arial 20,XY,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, not at all.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:50.25,0:20:55.23,main arial 20,XY,0000,0000,0000,,I befriended you because I knew \Nyou were that type of man.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:55.23,0:20:57.64,main arial 20,SB,0000,0000,0000,,I'm not your damn friend!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:57.64,0:20:58.89,main arial 20,SB,0000,0000,0000,,How many times do I need to say it?!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:58.89,0:21:02.70,main arial 20,XY,0000,0000,0000,,I'd say you have bigger concerns \Nthan worrying about me,
Dialogue: 0,0:21:02.70,0:21:05.85,main arial 20,XY,0000,0000,0000,,because it seems that Wú Shēng has \Ntaken quite an interest in you.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:05.85,0:21:10.25,main arial 20,XY,0000,0000,0000,,He might try and kill you once \Nhe's taken my head, you know.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:10.71,0:21:13.29,main arial 20,SB,0000,0000,0000,,I'll think about that\Nas we go along, I guess.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:13.85,0:21:16.24,main arial 20,XY,0000,0000,0000,,I imagine Juǎn will be quite disappointed.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:16.24,0:21:20.70,main arial 20,XY,0000,0000,0000,,He seemed to be looking forward \Nto the duel of his lifetime.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:20.70,0:21:24.25,main arial 20,SB,0000,0000,0000,,Gotta ask, why'd you stop us back there?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:27.02,0:21:30.21,main arial 20,SB,0000,0000,0000,,On the off chance I had won that duel,
Dialogue: 0,0:21:30.21,0:21:34.69,main arial 20,SB,0000,0000,0000,,you would've gotten the Soul Echo Flute \Nwithout having to make that crazy deal.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:35.20,0:21:38.63,main arial 20,SB,0000,0000,0000,,You could've just waited \Nto see how it played out.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:38.63,0:21:44.07,main arial 20,XY,0000,0000,0000,,As I said before, I'd rather keep the group \Ntogether until we reach Seven Sins Tower.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:44.89,0:21:50.02,main arial 20,SB,0000,0000,0000,,Shòu Yún Xiāo's bow, Xíng Hài's song,\Nand the Soul Echo Flute...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:50.58,0:21:52.66,main arial 20,SB,0000,0000,0000,,You've got everything you need, don't you?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:52.66,0:21:54.38,main arial 20,SB,0000,0000,0000,,I'm not part of the equation.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:54.38,0:21:59.11,main arial 20,XY,0000,0000,0000,,Hardly. You have a task \Nthat only you can complete.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:59.11,0:22:02.14,main arial 20,XY,0000,0000,0000,,One important enough to make\Nme offer my head as collateral.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:02.14,0:22:03.53,main arial 20,SB,0000,0000,0000,,What the hell's that?
Dialogue: 0,0:22:03.53,0:22:05.49,main arial 20,XY,0000,0000,0000,,I'm not telling yet!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:05.49,0:22:11.26,main arial 20,XY,0000,0000,0000,,Although, if you swear to do it, \NI'd be willing to explain...
Dialogue: 0,0:22:11.26,0:22:15.26,main arial 20,SB,0000,0000,0000,,In other words, you're still \Ndead-set on using me somehow?
Dialogue: 0,0:22:15.26,0:22:18.03,main arial 20,XY,0000,0000,0000,,Think of it as the two of \Nus helping each other out.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:18.03,0:22:21.84,main arial 20,XY,0000,0000,0000,,It's a bumpy road up\Nthe Demon Spine Mountains...
Dialogue: 0,0:22:29.68,0:22:31.84,main arial 20,DM,0000,0000,0000,,You summoned me, Master?
Dialogue: 0,0:22:31.84,0:22:34.35,main arial 20,MT,0000,0000,0000,,Have you found the the \NHù Yìn Shī girl yet?
Dialogue: 0,0:22:34.63,0:22:36.37,main arial 20,DM,0000,0000,0000,,I'm sorry, sir.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:36.37,0:22:40.25,main arial 20,DM,0000,0000,0000,,I've dedicated more men to the search, but...
Dialogue: 0,0:22:41.08,0:22:41.86,main arial 20,MT,0000,0000,0000,,No.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:42.59,0:22:46.26,main arial 20,MT,0000,0000,0000,,It may be a waste of time \Ntrying to search for them.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:47.03,0:22:47.77,main arial 20,DM,0000,0000,0000,,Sir?
Dialogue: 0,0:22:48.21,0:22:53.74,main arial 20,MT,0000,0000,0000,,Just as they have the Tiān Xing \NJiàn's guard, I have its handle.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:53.74,0:22:56.44,main arial 20,MT,0000,0000,0000,,If we both wish to complete it,
Dialogue: 0,0:22:56.44,0:23:00.81,main arial 20,MT,0000,0000,0000,,then won't they be coming to us?
Dialogue: 0,0:23:01.50,0:23:03.60,main arial 20,DM,0000,0000,0000,,To Seven Sins Tower?!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:03.60,0:23:07.38,main arial 20,DM,0000,0000,0000,,I can't imagine it.\NAre they truly that foolish?
